title: This TV Actress’ Latest Photoshoot Is Too Hot To Handle
text:
Swagata Dam Mar . 31 . 2017 
Just a while ago, I had shared some super hot photos of TV diva Karishma Sharma from her Instagram page. And this morning, I came across a couple of her new pictures clicked by photographer Amit Khanna , where she looks sexier than ever. Check these out. A post shared by Amit Khannaphotography (@amitkhannaphotography) on Mar 30, 2017 at 8:30am PDT A post shared by Amit Khannaphotography (@amitkhannaphotography) on Mar 29, 2017 at 10:02pm PDT
